Dexterity, in regards to amount of crits they are pure eye candy IMO, they change damage output by maybe 1% overall and can get shaman buffs on most any large scale raids. Procs can increase agro but each wepon seems to have its own proc rate already set to a degree, I had some fun with a guildmate with a Earthshaker I gave him awhile ago and that sucker procd on 1/2 the jousting runs it hit me, somehow I dont think a paladin had 255 dex to make it proc that much.<br>
